Windrop is a Cygwin port of Eggdrop IRC Bot

windrop-1.9.5-20230803.exe is a 7-Zip self-extracting archive

sha256sum windrop-1.9.5-20230803.exe 2cff1e3ac32e748635bda161c4a2709f117a359888ee869301721ac5152f506f

This Eggdrop / Windrop v1.9.5 includes:
- eggdrop 1.9.5 https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop
- patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1406
- patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1435
- patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1444
- patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1460
- botnetop 1.4 module https://github.com/michaelortmann/botnetop.mod
- gseen 1.4.1 module https://github.com/michaelortmann/gseen.mod
- stats 1.7 module https://github.com/michaelortmann/stats.mod
- unbound 1.0 module https://github.com/michaelortmann/unbound.mod
- openssl 3.1.2 https://www.openssl.org
- tcl 8.6.13 plus patches https://github.com/tcltk/tcl/tree/core-8-6-branch
- unbound 1.17.1 plus patches (IPV6_MTU and libtool)
- zlib 1.2.13 https://www.zlib.net/
- cygwin 3.4.7 https://cygwin.com/
- 64 bit

Last official Windrop release was Windrop 1.8.3, so this alternative was
created until hopefully the official Windrop team resumes pushing out new
versions.

Eggdrop: https://www.eggheads.org
Windrop: https://windrop.sourceforge.net

How to compile Windrop 1.9.5:

Install Cygwin, select packages:
- autoconf2.7 2.71-2
- automake1.16 1.16.5-1
- binutils 2.41-1
- gcc-core 11.4.0-1
- git 2.39.0-1
- make 4.4.1-2
- mingw64-x86_64-gcc-core 11.4.0-1
- cygwins openssl can be used:
  openssl 1.1.1u-1 and libssl-devel 1.1.1u-1
  but i compiled openssl 3.1.0 instead
- cygwins tcl can be used:
  tcl 8.6.12-1 and tcl-devel 8.6.12-1
  but i compiled tcl 8.6.13 instead
- zlib-devel 1.2.13-1
- libexpat-devel 2.5.0-1, if you want unbound mod
- libtool 2.4.7-1, if you want unbound mod
- patch 2.7.6.17, if you want unbound mod

Compile OpenSSL 3.1.2:
$ curl -O https://www.openssl.org/source/openssl-3.1.2
$ tar -zxvf openssl-3.1.2.tar.gz
$ cd openssl-3.1.2
$ ./config --prefix=/opt/openssl-3.1.2
$ make
$ make install

Compile Tcl 8.6:
$ git clone https://github.com/tcltk/tcl.git
$ cd tcl
# tcl 8.6.13 doesnt compile under cygwin. workaround is using bleeding edge tcl 8.6 from https://github.com/tcltk/tcl/tree/core-8-6-branch
# commit f632ecb40650fc82b537e938435e44e2c1f2fb14 (fix generic/tcl.h and eliminate the need for --enable-64bit) would suffice but i used core-8-6-branch, which has more crash and windows fixes
$ git checkout core-8-6-branch
# as of time of this writing core-8-6-branch is commit cb7eb97a8df1898896375054b44b9d6519b970e4 from 20230801
$ cd unix
$ ./configure --prefix=/opt/tcl-8.6
$ make
$ make install

Compile Unbound 1.17.1
$ curl -O https://www.nlnetlabs.nl/downloads/unbound/unbound-1.17.1.tar.gz
$ tar -zxvf unbound-1.17.1.tar.gz
$ cd unbound-1.17.1
$ patch -p1 -i ../unbound.patch
$ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/openssl-3.1.2/lib libtool=libtool ./configure --prefix=/opt/unbound-1.17.1 --with-ssl=/opt/openssl-3.1.2
$ make
$ make install

Compile Eggdrop 1.9.5:
$ git clone https://github.com/michaelortmann/eggdrop.git
# as of time of this writing master branch develop is commit f51443f52bc5c9d46d717042a83918961e1b4fea from 20230709
# apply patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1406
$ git cherry-pick ..0c48844ca51ef7ad8355b29c44f7f903da9928c5
# apply patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1435
$ git cherry-pick ..fb9c9ed980f61fbae21c4db6224904a7b199ec90
# apply patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1444
$ git cherry-pick ..ccba4f94d19399162cadf57a13dd17869b9ba29d
# apply patch https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/pull/1460
$ git cherry-pick ..42eb9a61745fcab48f7aeb50e6e91a1af9bfaa08
$ vi src/version.h
# define EGG_PATCH "windrop-20230803"
$ cd src/mod
$ git clone https://github.com/michaelortmann/botnetop.mod.git
$ git clone https://github.com/michaelortmann/gseen.mod.git 
$ git clone https://github.com/michaelortmann/stats.mod.git
$ git clone https://github.com/michaelortmann/unbound.mod.git
$ cd ../..
$ CFLAGS="-I/opt/unbound-1.17.1/include -L/opt/unbound-1.17.1/lib -O2" ./configure --prefix=/opt/windrop-1.9.5-20230803 --enable-strip --with-ssllib=/opt/openssl-3.1.2/lib --with-sslinc=/opt/openssl-3.1.2/include --with-tcllib=/opt/tcl-8.6/lib/libtcl8.6.dll.a --with-tclinc=/opt/tcl-8.6/include/tcl.h 
$ make config
$ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/openssl-3.1.2/lib:/opt/tcl-8.6/lib PATH=$PATH:/opt/openssl-3.1.2/bin:/opt/tcl-8.6/bin make eggdrop
$ LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/openssl-3.1.2/lib:/opt/tcl-8.6/lib PATH=$PATH:/opt/openssl-3.1.2/bin:/opt/tcl-8.6/bin make install
$ EGG=/opt/windrop-1.9.5-20230803
$ cp src/mod/botnetop.mod/botnetop.conf $EGG
$ cp src/mod/gseen.mod/gseen.conf $EGG
$ cp src/mod/stats.mod/stats.conf $EGG
$ cp -r src/mod/stats.mod/templates $EGG
$ cd $EGG
$ rm eggdrop.exe
$ mv eggdrop.exe-1.9.5 eggdrop.exe
$ rm -rf modules
$ mv modules-1.9.5 modules
$ cp /opt/openssl-3.1.2/bin/cygcrypto-3.dll .
$ cp /opt/openssl-3.1.2/bin/cygssl-3.dll .
$ cp /bin/cygwin1.dll .
$ cp /bin/cygz.dll .
$ cp /opt/tcl-8.6/bin/libtcl8.6.dll .
$ mkdir lib
$ cp -r /opt/tcl-8.6/lib/tcl8 lib
$ cp -r /opt/tcl-8.6/lib/tcl8.6 lib
$ cp /opt/unbound-1.17.1/bin/cygunbound-8.dll .

